<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <title>{% block title %}MeetOUT - Home{% endblock %}</title>
        {% block stylesheets %}
            <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css/styles.css') }}"/>
            <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css/hover-min.css') }}"/>
            <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto" rel="stylesheet">
            <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat" rel="stylesheet">
        {% endblock %}
        <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="{{ asset('favicon.ico') }}" />
    </head>
    <body class="homepage">
        {% block body %}

            <header class="home-head">
                {% block header %}
                    <ul class="header-home">
                        <li><img src="{{ asset('img/logo.png') }}" alt="MeetOut logo"/></li>
                        <li><button type="button" class="hvr-shrink" id="b-isesion">Iniciar sesión</button></li>
                    </ul>

                {% endblock %}
            </header>

            <div class="content">
                <section id="hizq">
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aenean fringilla, libero at ornare sodales, tellus turpis faucibus purus, eu suscipit nisl quam a felis. Cras blandit tempus purus vitae facilisis.
